The paper discusses document classification, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of data mining and machine learning techniques such as expectation maximization and semi-supervised learning suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the use of a dataset and evaluation metrics suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the field of databases (cs.DB).
